{"tid":607733,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2018韓國福布斯名人榜 IU總榜第五","createTime":"2018-03-27T14:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T14:52:26.000Z","uid":34643,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ac111d2d3820e3de0eb3a40ca8c4d83deccbc9d8","tid":607733,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:01:50.000Z","msg":"韓國福布斯18年4月刊以&ldquo;照耀世界的你的星&rdquo;為題公布了&ldquo;2018韓國福布斯名人榜&rdquo;。IU列總體第五，單人第一，Solo歌手第一！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OZQ35sH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOZQ35sH.jpg&h=1525a992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n細項排名上，IU收入列第十，媒體影響力列第三，放送影響力列第六。<br />\n<br />\n福布斯寫道：&ldquo;從2009年開始每年進行的韓國福布斯名人榜選定，今年迎來了第十回。不通過人氣投票，而是以客觀的數據為基礎，測算明星的影響力的該榜，被韓國主要媒體一致引用而具極高信賴性。從十年以來所選定的名單中，能讀取韓國文體界的大勢變化&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n本次是IU第五次進入Top0，其余四次為2012年列第三，2013年第八，2014年第十，2016年第九。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AexjPiK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAexjPiK.jpg&h=f873c6f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"619e451730a5517d24528149727b04428bb4944e","tid":607733,"uid":89595,"like":14,"dislike":8,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:03:11.000Z","msg":"Who fucking cares<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e4c1a7327999ce55441e7a33cedb8ddbe1ba31","tid":607733,"uid":158947,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實力"},{"pid":"efad0b4aa030d7c60925241e0352f4304ab15935","tid":607733,"uid":52984,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/222743_d2ced6682880a8157ecd0fb9e2eca021.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum